    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/7d718d4db8c9e72a3015eb28510980a6.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br>When is it time to move on? Before your ex gets married to someone else… right?<br><br>You play as Alex, a struggling musician invited to his ex-girlfriend Emily's wedding. It's in Turkey. It's in one month. You said you'd bring a plus-one… so the countdown's on, because you don't have one.<br><br>Filmed in live action, you see through Alex's eyes as he makes decisions that can land him just about anywhere as he tries to find his ideal date for the wedding. The trouble is, Alex doesn't have much money, and it seems like everyone who offers to help is also conspiring against him ... which is to say, YOU!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/923c19c99cfb04c60e808ea0b7ac6668.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>Alex meets many colorful characters throughout his journey to Emily's wedding. The decisions you make along the way matter – some will bring him closer to love, while others will push it further from his reach. Who will you choose?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/a9606feeb32f23492fcdeda394e5bf2e.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/54ec06e4ecfcb56d22f24f2e04484c24.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/54ec06e4ecfcb56d22f24f2e04484c24.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/54ec06e4ecfcb56d22f24f2e04484c24.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Irena, Alex’s classmate from college, is also in town for Emily's wedding. Alex has been searching far and wide for his date, but he hasn't noticed the ideal partner right in front of him. Irena cares deeply for Alex's well-being, but will this blossom into romantic love?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/a9883e98cc79ba3825a947dbd4627a66.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/20261707e8a51785245395ffeeca1f33.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/20261707e8a51785245395ffeeca1f33.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/20261707e8a51785245395ffeeca1f33.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Danica has always been “one of the boys”, but realizes after meeting Alex that her prickly exterior will only take her so far when it comes to love. She may be his friend's sister, but that doesn’t mean Alex shouldn’t shoot his shot, right?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/6c3f3805469113b591e58c5733e72ad8.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/b9c3a0edc6463c0bf01791144319cb66.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/b9c3a0edc6463c0bf01791144319cb66.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/b9c3a0edc6463c0bf01791144319cb66.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Rana is the &quot;coffee girl&quot; at The Terrance, and Sofia’s roommate. Quiet, unassuming, and often overlooked, Alex may well be the man to give her a deserved moment in the sun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/02875b02e1068cbfb68c3c2a1ef1ee58.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/5fdfff0ef3b606ddb56f4a12d2db61bf.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/5fdfff0ef3b606ddb56f4a12d2db61bf.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/5fdfff0ef3b606ddb56f4a12d2db61bf.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Sofia is an A-list model who wants nothing more than to succeed… until Alex comes along. Her “no dating” rule stands in the way, but rules are meant to be broken, right? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/fe9162a8de7ecb1a1b902e69491854b8.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/470881ee022f0a63ec5788d64f41f1ee.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/470881ee022f0a63ec5788d64f41f1ee.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/470881ee022f0a63ec5788d64f41f1ee.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Blaire is always around, but ever out of reach. She is drawn to Alex's charms, but this mysterious girl may be too much for him to handle. She will try to romance him whether he likes it or not.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/a1c14f55d493afbe2ead9aec4b938d85.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ba4c5a6b1a71ddae34e8ff32b4a96bad.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ba4c5a6b1a71ddae34e8ff32b4a96bad.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ba4c5a6b1a71ddae34e8ff32b4a96bad.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Alex aims to find his true love, but a sea of enticing sirens keeps steering him away; Gizem the bossy divorcee, Elif the benevolent nurse, Halima the rattlesnake, and Suzan the mature, older woman (mother of Danica and Damir)… <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/ac5483abe34f4162a7e8d145694c39ad.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/4085b174fe960f5955037b6768f5f8f1.poster.avif?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/4085b174fe960f5955037b6768f5f8f1.webm?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/4085b174fe960f5955037b6768f5f8f1.mp4?t=1730833344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014690/extras/730fbe15895ab8e7183222c9fefc4591.webp?t=1730833344\" width=616 height=20 /></span><br>Alex wants to find a date, but not everyone Alex meets wants to help. His friend Damir loves him like a brother, but can’t stop getting into trouble. There's also Valko, the bar owner turned gang leader, Burak the band bully, and worst of all, the overly nice and cordial Kerem… his ex-girlfriend's fiancé! How can Alex find his true love at a time like this?",
